@MortenStryhn @EUCouncil @MalmstromEU @Trade_EU @danielrosarioEU Dear @MortenStryhn 
Singapore is an important gateway to the whole Asia-Pacific area.  @ASEAN member Singapore is the base for over 10.000 EU companies that use it as a hub to serve the whole Pacific Rim.

Europe is open for business!
